{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":619,"text":"On March 14, this year,"},{"time":3418,"text":"I posted this poster on Facebook."},{"time":6298,"text":"This is an image of me and my daughter"},{"time":8723,"text":"holding the Israeli flag."},{"time":11503,"text":"I will try to explain to you about the context of why"},{"time":14542,"text":"and when I posted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17148,"text":"A few days ago, I was sitting waiting"},{"time":20269,"text":"on the line at the grocery store,"},{"time":22573,"text":"and the owner and one of the clients"},{"time":25859,"text":"were talking to each other,"},{"time":27549,"text":"and the owner was explaining to the client"},{"time":29607,"text":"that we're going to get 10,000 missiles on Israel."},{"time":33083,"text":"And the client was saying, no, it's 10,000 a day."},{"time":37796,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40457,"text":"(\"10,000 missiles\") This is the context. This is where we are now in Israel."},{"time":45458,"text":"We have this war with Iran coming for 10 years now,"},{"time":49046,"text":"and we have people, you know, afraid."},{"time":52421,"text":"It's like every year it's the last minute"},{"time":55984,"text":"that we can do something about the war with Iran."},{"time":58459,"text":"It's like, if we don't act now, it's too late forever,"},{"time":62131,"text":"for 10 years now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64383,"text":"So at some point it became, you know, to me,"},{"time":66780,"text":"I'm a graphic designer, so I made posters about it"},{"time":69830,"text":"and I posted the one I just showed you before."},{"time":73805,"text":"Most of the time, I make posters, I post them on Facebook,"},{"time":76867,"text":"my friends like it, don't like it,"},{"time":78524,"text":"most of the time don't like it, don't share it,"},{"time":80255,"text":"don't nothing,"},{"time":82478,"text":"and it's another day."},{"time":84471,"text":"So I went to sleep, and that was it for me."},{"time":88423,"text":"And later on in the night, I woke up"},{"time":91339,"text":"because I'm always waking up in the night,"},{"time":93172,"text":"and I went by the computer and I see all these red dots,"},{"time":95747,"text":"you know, on Facebook, which I've never seen before."},{"time":98899,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":99982,"text":"And I was like, \"What's going on?\""},{"time":102319,"text":"So I come to the computer and I start looking on,"},{"time":105823,"text":"and suddenly I see many people talking to me,"},{"time":108848,"text":"most of them I don't know,"},{"time":111211,"text":"and a few of them from Iran,"},{"time":113796,"text":"which is -- What?"},{"time":117277,"text":"Because you have to understand,"},{"time":119894,"text":"in Israel we don't talk with people from Iran."},{"time":123548,"text":"We don't know people from Iran."},{"time":125518,"text":"It's like, on Facebook, you have friends only from --"},{"time":129883,"text":"it's like your neighbors are your friends on Facebook."},{"time":133337,"text":"And now people from Iran are talking to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136074,"text":"So I start answering this girl, and she's telling me"},{"time":139583,"text":"she saw the poster and she asked her family to come,"},{"time":144443,"text":"because they don't have a computer, she asked her family"},{"time":146059,"text":"to come to see the poster, and they're all sitting in the living room crying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150607,"text":"So I'm like, whoa."},{"time":152289,"text":"I ask my wife to come, and I tell her, you have to see that."},{"time":155707,"text":"People are crying, and she came, she read the text,"},{"time":158756,"text":"and she started to cry."},{"time":161456,"text":"And everybody's crying now. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164094,"text":"So I don't know what to do, so my first reflex,"},{"time":166894,"text":"as a graphic designer, is, you know, to show everybody"},{"time":170208,"text":"what I'd just seen, and people started to see them"},{"time":173906,"text":"and to share them, and that's how it started."},{"time":176506,"text":"The day after, when really it became a lot of talking,"},{"time":180245,"text":"I said to myself, and my wife said to me,"},{"time":182468,"text":"I also want a poster,"},{"time":183734,"text":"so this is her. (Laughter)"},{"time":187196,"text":"Because it's working, put me in a poster now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192178,"text":"But more seriously, I was like, okay, these ones work,"},{"time":195288,"text":"but it's not just about me, it's about people from Israel"},{"time":198586,"text":"who want to say something."},{"time":199489,"text":"So I'm going to shoot all the people I know, if they want,"},{"time":202326,"text":"and I'm going to put them in a poster and I'm going to share them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204414,"text":"So I went to my neighbors and friends and students"},{"time":208096,"text":"and I just asked them, give me a picture, I will make you a poster."},{"time":212187,"text":"And that's how it started. And that's how, really,"},{"time":215084,"text":"it's unleashed, because suddenly people"},{"time":218497,"text":"from Facebook, friends and others,"},{"time":220947,"text":"just understand that they can be part of it."},{"time":223904,"text":"It's not just one dude making one poster,"},{"time":225638,"text":"it's -- we can be part of it, so they start sending me pictures"},{"time":229151,"text":"and ask me, \"Make me a poster. Post it."},{"time":231527,"text":"Tell the Iranians we from Israel love you too.\""},{"time":236161,"text":"It became, you know, at some point it was really, really intense."},{"time":239529,"text":"I mean, so many pictures, so I asked friends"},{"time":243844,"text":"to come, graphic designers most of them,"},{"time":246967,"text":"to make posters with me, because I didn't have the time."},{"time":249570,"text":"It was a huge amount of pictures."},{"time":252226,"text":"So for a few days, that's how my living room was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255621,"text":"And we received Israeli posters, Israeli images,"},{"time":260144,"text":"but also lots of comments, lots of messages from Iran."},{"time":264830,"text":"And we took these messages and we made posters out of it,"},{"time":268512,"text":"because I know people: They don't read, they see images."},{"time":271977,"text":"If it's an image, they may read it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274953,"text":"So here are a few of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277670,"text":"(\"You are my first Israelian friend. I wish we both get rid of our idiot politicians, anyway nice to see you!\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":279943,"text":"(\"I love that blue. I love that star. I love that flag.\") This one is really moving for me because it's the story"},{"time":283479,"text":"of a girl who has been raised in Iran"},{"time":287293,"text":"to walk on an Israeli flag to enter her school every morning,"},{"time":292571,"text":"and now that she sees the posters that we're sending,"},{"time":295902,"text":"she starts -- she said that she changed her mind,"},{"time":298577,"text":"and now she loves that blue, she loves that star,"},{"time":301918,"text":"and she loves that flag, talking about the Israeli flag,"},{"time":304253,"text":"and she wished that we'd meet and come to visit one another,"},{"time":308073,"text":"and just a few days after I posted the first poster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313156,"text":"The day after,"},{"time":315768,"text":"Iranians started to respond with their own posters."},{"time":318485,"text":"They have graphic designers. What? (Laughter)"},{"time":321911,"text":"Crazy, crazy."},{"time":324253,"text":"So you can see they are still shy, they don't want to show their faces,"},{"time":327778,"text":"but they want to spread the message."},{"time":329350,"text":"They want to respond. They want to say the same thing."},{"time":331486,"text":"So. And now it's communication."},{"time":334591,"text":"It's a two-way story. It's Israelis and Iranians"},{"time":338017,"text":"sending the same message, one to each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340673,"text":"(\"My Israeli Friends. I don't hate you. I don't want War.\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":342351,"text":"This never happened before, and this is two people"},{"time":346511,"text":"supposed to be enemies, we're on the verge of a war,"},{"time":349428,"text":"and suddenly people on Facebook are starting to say,"},{"time":352047,"text":"\"I like this guy. I love those guys.\""},{"time":356198,"text":"And it became really big at some point."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360636,"text":"And then it became news."},{"time":363948,"text":"Because when you're seeing the Middle East, you see only the bad news."},{"time":368148,"text":"And suddenly, there is something that was happening"},{"time":370447,"text":"that was good news. So the guys on the news,"},{"time":373273,"text":"they say, \"Okay, let's talk about this.\""},{"time":374961,"text":"And they just came, and it was so much,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":378160,"text":"I remember one day, Michal,"},{"time":380599,"text":"she was talking with the journalist, and she was asking him,"},{"time":383399,"text":"\"Who's gonna see the show?\"And he said, \"Everybody.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":387457,"text":"So she said, \"Everybody in Palestine, in where? Israel?"},{"time":392954,"text":"Who is everybody?\"\"Everybody.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":395870,"text":"They said, \"Syria?\" \"Syria.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":397484,"text":"\"Lebanon?\"\"Lebanon.\""},{"time":399224,"text":"At some point, he just said, \"40 million people are going to see you today."},{"time":403195,"text":"It's everybody.\" The Chinese."},{"time":405907,"text":"And we were just at the beginning of the story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411533,"text":"Something crazy also happened."},{"time":413615,"text":"Every time a country started talking about it,"},{"time":416803,"text":"like Germany, America, wherever,"},{"time":420072,"text":"a page on Facebook popped up with the same logo"},{"time":425500,"text":"with the same stories, so at the beginning"},{"time":427257,"text":"we had \"Iran-Loves-Israel,\" which is an Iranian"},{"time":431072,"text":"sitting in Tehran, saying, \"Okay, Israel loves Iran?"},{"time":436150,"text":"I give you Iran-Loves-Israel.\""},{"time":438060,"text":"You have Palestine-Loves-Israel."},{"time":439662,"text":"You have Lebanon that just -- a few days ago."},{"time":442290,"text":"And this whole list of pages on Facebook"},{"time":445758,"text":"dedicated to the same message,"},{"time":447858,"text":"to people sending their love, one to each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453695,"text":"The moment I really understood that something was happening,"},{"time":457391,"text":"a friend of mine told me,"},{"time":459841,"text":"\"Google the word 'Israel.'\""},{"time":461843,"text":"And those were the first images on those days"},{"time":465550,"text":"that popped up from Google"},{"time":467829,"text":"when you were typing, \"Israel\" or \"Iran.\""},{"time":471435,"text":"We really changed how people see the Middle East."},{"time":475749,"text":"Because you're not in the Middle East."},{"time":477518,"text":"You're somewhere over there, and then you want to see the Middle East,"},{"time":479809,"text":"so you go on Google and you say, \"Israel,\""},{"time":481465,"text":"and they give you the bad stuff."},{"time":482674,"text":"And for a few days you got those images."},{"time":487443,"text":"Today the Israel-Loves-Iran page"},{"time":489842,"text":"is this number, 80,831, and two million people last week"},{"time":495230,"text":"went on the page and shared, liked, I don't know,"},{"time":498093,"text":"commented on one of the photos."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500685,"text":"So for five months now, that's what we are doing,"},{"time":505193,"text":"me, Michal, a few of my friends, are just making images."},{"time":509943,"text":"We're showing a new reality"},{"time":512230,"text":"by just making images"},{"time":514433,"text":"because that's how the world perceives us."},{"time":517330,"text":"They see images of us, and they see bad images."},{"time":520131,"text":"So we're working on making good images. End of story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525182,"text":"Look at this one. This is the Iran-Loves-Israel page."},{"time":530097,"text":"This is not the Israel-Loves-Iran. This is not my page."},{"time":532615,"text":"This is a guy in Tehran on the day of remembrance"},{"time":536394,"text":"of the Israeli fallen soldier"},{"time":538936,"text":"putting an image of an Israeli soldier on his page."},{"time":542899,"text":"This is the enemy."},{"time":546290,"text":"What?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":547762,"text":"(\"Our heartfelt condolences to the families who lost their dearests in terror attack in Bulgaria\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":549804,"text":"And it's going both ways."},{"time":551509,"text":"It's like, we are showing respect, one to each other."},{"time":556047,"text":"And we're understanding. And you show compassion."},{"time":561033,"text":"And you become friends."},{"time":565794,"text":"And at some point, you become friends on Facebook,"},{"time":569021,"text":"and you become friends in life."},{"time":570798,"text":"You can go and travel and meet people."},{"time":573614,"text":"And I was in Munich a few weeks ago."},{"time":576992,"text":"I went there to open an exposition about Iran"},{"time":580819,"text":"and I met there with people from the page"},{"time":583276,"text":"that told me, \"Okay, you're going to be in Europe,"},{"time":585582,"text":"I'm coming. I'm coming from France, from Holland,"},{"time":588186,"text":"from Germany,\" of course, and from Israel people came,"},{"time":590907,"text":"and we just met there for the first time in real life."},{"time":595482,"text":"I met with people that are supposed to be my enemies"},{"time":599999,"text":"for the first time. And we just shake hands,"},{"time":602613,"text":"and have a coffee and a nice discussion,"},{"time":604616,"text":"and we talk about food and basketball."},{"time":607336,"text":"And that was the end of it."},{"time":609074,"text":"Remember that image from the beginning?"},{"time":611828,"text":"At some point we met in real life, and we became friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620209,"text":"And it goes the other way around."},{"time":622873,"text":"Some girl that we met on Facebook"},{"time":625666,"text":"never been in Israel, born and raised in Iran,"},{"time":628576,"text":"lives in Germany, afraid of Israelis"},{"time":632134,"text":"because of what she knows about us,"},{"time":634364,"text":"decides after a few months of talking on the Internet"},{"time":637978,"text":"with some Israelis to come to Israel,"},{"time":641022,"text":"and she gets on the plane and arrives at Ben Gurion"},{"time":645519,"text":"and says, \"Okay, not that big a deal.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":651646,"text":"So a few weeks ago, the stress is getting higher,"},{"time":655233,"text":"so we start this new campaign"},{"time":657706,"text":"called \"Not ready to die in your war.\""},{"time":661078,"text":"I mean, it's plus/minus the same message,"},{"time":663891,"text":"but we wanted really to add some aggressivity to it."},{"time":667565,"text":"And again, something amazing happened,"},{"time":670516,"text":"something that we didn't have on the first wave of the campaign."},{"time":673854,"text":"Now people from Iran, the same ones who were shy"},{"time":678124,"text":"at the first campaign and just sent, you know,"},{"time":680229,"text":"their foot and half their faces,"},{"time":682417,"text":"now they're sending their faces, and they're saying,"},{"time":684817,"text":"\"Okay, no problem, we're into it. We are with you.\""},{"time":693882,"text":"Just read where those guys are from."},{"time":697402,"text":"And for every guy from Israel,"},{"time":699717,"text":"you've got someone from Iran."},{"time":711084,"text":"Just people sending their pictures."},{"time":731131,"text":"Crazy, yes?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":733314,"text":"So --"},{"time":734950,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":744207,"text":"So you may ask yourself, who is this dude?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":751604,"text":"My name is Ronny Edry, and I'm 41, I'm an Israeli,"},{"time":755258,"text":"I'm a father of two, I'm a husband,"},{"time":759538,"text":"and I'm a graphic designer. I'm teaching graphic design."},{"time":764518,"text":"And I'm not that naive, because a lot of the time"},{"time":768286,"text":"I've been asked, many times I've been asked, \"Yeah, but,"},{"time":771669,"text":"this is really naive, sending flowers over, I mean — \""}]},{"cues":[{"time":774895,"text":"I was in the army. I was in the paratroopers for three years,"},{"time":778946,"text":"and I know how it looks from the ground."},{"time":782496,"text":"I know how it can look really bad."},{"time":786822,"text":"So to me, this is the courageous thing to do,"},{"time":790959,"text":"to try to reach the other side before it's too late,"},{"time":794398,"text":"because when it's going to be too late, it's going to be too late."},{"time":796313,"text":"And sometimes war is inevitable, sometimes,"},{"time":800734,"text":"but maybe [with] effort, we can avoid it."},{"time":804804,"text":"Maybe as people, because especially in Israel,"},{"time":808159,"text":"we're in a democracy. We have the freedom of speech,"},{"time":811572,"text":"and maybe that little thing can change something."},{"time":815015,"text":"And really, we can be our own ambassadors."},{"time":819360,"text":"We can just send a message and hope for the best."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826096,"text":"So I want to ask Michal, my wife, to come with me"},{"time":828438,"text":"on the stage just to make with you one image,"},{"time":833218,"text":"because it's all about images."},{"time":835343,"text":"And maybe that image will help us change something."},{"time":839914,"text":"Just raise that. Exactly."},{"time":843421,"text":"And I'm just going to take a picture of it,"},{"time":845922,"text":"and I'm just going to post it on Facebook"},{"time":848724,"text":"with kind of \"Israelis for peace\" or something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":856640,"text":"Oh my God."},{"time":859150,"text":"Don't cry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":861512,"text":"Thank you guys."},{"time":863203,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}